articles.title: Dog-eating crocodile that terrorized Australian town is killed and eaten by residents: "Never a dull moment" - CBS News
articles.description: The 12-foot reptile "had been stalking and lunging out of the water at children and adults," police said.
articles.content: A saltwater crocodile terrorized a remote Australian community by snapping up dogs and lunging at kids -- only to meet its end in a feast cooked up by locals. The 12-foot reptile "had been stalking a… [+2133 chars]
